select `customer_orders`.*, `c`.*, `c`.`address` as `customer_add`, `customer_orders`.`address` as `delivery_address`, `u`.`username` as `username`, `customer_orders`.`created_at` as `order_created_date` from `customer_orders` left join `customers` as `c` on `c`.`customer_id` = `customer_orders`.`customer_id` left join `users` as `u` on `u`.`user_id` = `customer_orders`.`user_id` where `customer_orders`.`type` = 'outward' and `customer_orders`.`customer_order_id` = '29591' and `customer_orders`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1

select `order_items`.*, `i`.`name` as `item_name`, `m`.`name` as `marka_name`, `f`.`number` as `floor_number`, `g`.`number` as `grid_number`, `c`.`number` as `chamber_number`, (SELECT sum(if(oi.type='inward',oi.quantity,0))-sum(if(oi.type='outward',oi.quantity,0)) FROM order_items as oi WHERE oi.vakkal_number = order_items.vakkal_number and oi.item_id=order_items.item_id and oi.sort <= order_items.sort) AS balance_quantity from `order_items` left join `customer_orders` as `co` on `co`.`customer_order_id` = `order_items`.`customer_order_id` left join `items` as `i` on `i`.`item_id` = `order_items`.`item_id` left join `floor` as `f` on `f`.`floor_id` = `order_items`.`floor_id` left join `grid` as `g` on `g`.`grid_id` = `order_items`.`grid_id` left join `chamber` as `c` on `c`.`chamber_id` = `order_items`.`chamber_id` left join `marka` as `m` on `m`.`marka_id` = `order_items`.`marka_id` where `co`.`customer_order_id` = '29591' and `co`.`type` = 'outward' and `order_items`.`deleted_at` is null order by `order_items`.`order_item_id` asc
